text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It captures the extent to which women are free
from forced labor, have property rights and access to the justice system, and enjoy freedoms of movement. The variables ranges from 0 to 1
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
